Credio Client for PHP

Credio website - http://www.crediosys.com


Table of Contents:
    1) Introduction
    2) Installation
    3) Usage


1) Introduction

Use Credio Client for PHP to implement Credio API within Your PHP application.


2) Installation:

2.1) Credio PHP Client - copy CredioClient.php and CredioClientError.php to Your application.
2.2) Examples - copy CredioClient*.php together with examples folder in some_folder under your web_root.
open URL http://yourwebsite.com/some_folder/examples


3) Usage:

3.1) get Instance of Credio\Client
3.2) use Instance